\Gamma(s)\Gamma(1-s)=\frac{\pi}{\sin(\pi s)}
 \Gamma(s)\Gamma(1-s)=2\int_0^{\pi/2}\tan^{2s-1}(x)\,\text dx\;\;(0<s<1) 
 2\int_0^{\pi/2}\tan^{2s-1}(x)\,\text dx=\frac{\pi}{\sin(\pi s)} 
 2\int_1^\infty\frac{1}{x(x^2-1)^{1-s}}\text dx=\int_1^\infty\frac{1}{x(x-1)^{1-s}}\text dx 
